==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea clam
<hw>Sea" clam`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of the
large bivalve mollusks found on the open seacoast, especially those of
the family <fam>Mactridae</fam>, as the common American species.
(<spn>Mactra solidissima</spn> or <spn>Spisula solidissima</spn>); --
called also <altname>beach clam</altname>, and <altname>surf
clam</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sea coal</ent>⟦br⟧
